{
  "stem": "1918.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And at the same time that she noticed this, the Nazis on the two sides went-- and the back-- went back to shoot two girls, I think, while one is digging the grave.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this gave my sister the opportunity to be unnoticed by the Germans who went back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And by this time, we were so badly off that we didn't talk to each other and didn't make plans to do everything together, but whoever can survive should.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she bolted and ran into the little house and up to the attic.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my little sister Regina also standing next to her saw her, and she ran.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I saw Regina, and I ran.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were certain that Zippy, our oldest sister, ran into the next house, but we could not go look for it-- for her until-- until we are free.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Chica went upstairs to the attic, and she yelled down at one point, and she said, 'Hey, are you all here?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I found a frozen cabbage, and it's delicious, and nobody's in the house.' And we yelled up and said, 'No.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There are only the two of us here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Zippy is probably in another house. ' And suddenly we heard, after this-- either prior or after this exchange, we heard the crackling of the snow, and the top dog came with his big German Shepard.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was coming back from the killing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was cursing, 'The goddamn Jews!",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "How dare they to-- they escape, and we have to go and bury them?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "How dare they?' And he was talking to himself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And all this time, while he's talking to himself, Regina and I are hiding in a little dog house that was emptied.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
